{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_12_01_short",
  "title": "成宮すず 1話 あんなのぴょーんですわ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "アリス！　私がアリスですわよ！\n『劇団★見』の主演ですわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alice! I am Alice‚ you know!\nThe leading star of “Troupe★Hoshimi” no less!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "聞いたぞ。今度のライブで、雫とすずのダブル主演で\n不思議の国のアリスがモチーフの舞台を演じるんだよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard. At the next live‚ you and Shizuku will be co-starring\nin a stage play themed around Alice in Wonderland‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "でも……大丈夫か？\n演技の経験は、以前連ドラに出演した一回きりだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… are you going to be okay?\nYour acting experience is limited to that one TV drama you did before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "今や私はBIG4！　つまりは大女優成宮すずですわ！\n不安は捨てて大船に乗った気持ちでいてくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am now one of the BIG4! In other words‚ the great actress Suzu Narumiya!\nCast aside your worries and sit back with complete confidence!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7611111004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "随分と大きく出たな\n大女優はさすがに言い過ぎじゃないか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re making some pretty bold claims.\n“Great actress” might be a bit much‚ don’t you think…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0333282471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "細かいことを言わないでくださいまし\n私のこの自信は過信ではありませんのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don’t nitpick over such trivial details.\nThis confidence of mine is not overconfidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8558907191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "なぜならこの私、不思議の国のアリスならば\n幼い頃に劇で演じたことがあるんですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because when it comes to Alice in Wonderland‚\nI played it on stage when I was little!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6558907191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだったのか……\nそれでその劇はどうだったんだ？　好評だったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see…\nSo how was that play? Was it well received?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}